{"tid":1843573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"還押手足想要筆友啊","createTime":"2020-01-26T09:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T18:06:49.000Z","uid":263730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99aa2fc66731c0f20b1e50898f522f054346d94e","tid":1843573,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"我啊哥佢而定還押左係荔枝角，佢話入面生活還好，係悶左啲，而且最少還押4個月，所以想招下筆友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但由於安全問題，冇收信既地址，暫時只會email收信下。我都唔知我部電腦安唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以及為左大家安全問題<strong>請勿</strong>談及任何敏感問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢平時鍾意睇動畫，月廚。鍾意黑之契約者啊，小圓，re0，GUNDAM特別鍾意00同UC，死亡筆記啊魯魯修啊SAO啊clannad都鍾意。<br />\n女角特別鍾意黑貞、公主、SABER。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA0，年紀上黎睇好快可以做魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打機鐘意玩Rainbow6。平時會飲下紅酒啊，威士忌咁。渣開電單車，但比popo拖走左&hellip;&hellip;唔知幾時拎得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排鐘意左做gym，而家係倉都繼續做下掌上壓深蹲咁。<br />\n<br />\n鍾意啲大大份、傻更更既動物，比如袋熊，水瀨。被捕前一晚仲同我研究緊袋熊啲屎點係你方形既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係連豬派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係連狗派。不過其實兩隻同腦魔都鍾意既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n email:　protesterdog2020@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\nＰ牌仔冇得推，見到唔想寫信都幫手推下啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933e320d14f6e933e7d9f31be749bcf8f0070c87","tid":1843573,"uid":279146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fd6867d1434c0d1af9066510ea9d818fe3b55242","tid":1843573,"uid":315082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99aa2fc66731c0f20b1e50898f522f054346d94e","tid":1843573,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T09: